{"tid":2142476,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇電盈出售nowTV比 6823香港電訊，訊訊？","createTime":"2020-08-06T12:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T07:41:33.000Z","uid":70888,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9e50ee12fc6cb7210a6dc36c20ddca7a805273","tid":2142476,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:11:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母信託公司加個nowTV係咩玩法？<br />\n我要穩定收息呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"6e6ec6fa16d445d3cda76b897ff84a0734219cd3","tid":2142476,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"【財華社訊】電訊盈科(00008-HK)公布，建議將Now TV業務營運商電訊盈科媒體轉讓予香港電訊(06823-HK)，代價2.5億美元(約19.5億港元)。此外，該公司亦進行PCCW OTT策略檢討，PCCW OTT在香港、東南亞及中東地區經營泛區域OTT(over-the-top)視像娛樂及音樂平台，包括「Viu」和「Moov」品牌。該公司將繼續積極評估各種策略選項，以支持PCCW OTT的持續增長，包括尋求通過PCCW OTT的潛在獨立上市，或通過策略夥伴對PCCW OTT作出額外投資，進一步向PCCW OTT引入第三方融資。<br />\n<br />\nNow TV上半年收入跌6%至12.7億元，受全球體育賽事暫停影響，除息、稅、折舊及攤銷前盈利(EBITDA)跌3%至約2億元。期內，OTT業務收入升14%至5億元，除息、稅、折舊及攤銷前虧損收窄66%至8100萬元。"},{"pid":"8dece532f5ac9f45282d0c83672d615565a12961","tid":2142476,"uid":35658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"方便拆細再賣"},{"pid":"d537319f40f69b7890cb81f5c2817a4343a4b3a2","tid":2142476,"uid":214580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"有咩分別"},{"pid":"1505cade44867c7a214b179e67885bb097efb5de","tid":2142476,"uid":19528,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />NOW蝕大錢"},{"pid":"7141e4dfb81a0bbd286c69a30f6bac3cd4f1a095","tid":2142476,"uid":29246,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:02.000Z","msg":"俾舊垃圾HKT, 到時有晒藉口減派息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de7bca76364a68e4132d18b07634fd5fb1e8bd4","tid":2142476,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:15:04.000Z","msg":"咁絕？應該準備減派息"},{"pid":"5f93